            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">
          Forum Coming Soon! üöß
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
          We're building an amazing community forum where makers can ask
          questions, share tips, showcase their work, and connect with fellow
          creators. This feature is currently under development and will be
          launching soon!
        </p>

        <!-- Features Preview -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 p-6 rounded-xl"
          >
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üí¨</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Discussion Boards</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
              Organized by categories like Electronics, Woodworking, Robotics,
              and more
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100 p-6 rounded-xl"
          >
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">‚ùì</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Q&A Support</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
              Get help from experienced makers and community experts
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-pink-100 p-6 rounded-xl"
          >
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üéØ</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Project Showcases</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
              Share your creations and get feedback from the community
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Notify Me Form -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">
            Get Notified When We Launch!
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Be among the first to join our community forum. We'll send you an
            email as soon as it's ready.
          </p>
          <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <input
              type="email"
              placeholder="Enter your email address"
              class="flex-1 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border-2 border-gray-300 focus:border-blue-500 focus:outline-none"
            />
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 text-white rounded-lg font-bold hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:scale-105"
            >
