                Category-Based Discussions
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Find discussions organized by topic - Electronics, Woodworking,
                3D Printing, and more. Easy to navigate and find exactly what
                you're looking for.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div
              class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <span class="text-2xl">‚≠ê</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900">
                Expert Badges & Reputation
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Earn badges and build reputation by helping others and sharing
                quality content. Recognize top contributors in the community.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div
              class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-pink-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <span class="text-2xl">üîç</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900">
                Advanced Search
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Powerful search functionality to find solutions to your
                problems. Search by keywords, categories, tags, and user
                contributions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div
              class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <span class="text-2xl">üîî</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900">
